aracterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"(이거, 이 경치! 하구미가 어릴 적에 본 놀이동산이다!\n그때는 하구미를 웃는 얼굴로 만들어줘서 고마웠어!\n오늘은 하구미가 웃는 얼굴로 만들어줄 차례야!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event57-15-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"(괜찮아! 하구미한테 맡겨줘!\n헬로해피 모두와 함께라면 어느 곳이든 웃는 얼굴로 만들 수 있어!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event57-15-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"(떠오르는 환희의 목소리와 넘치는 웃는 얼굴……\n아아, 세상은 덧없음으로 가득 차 있다……)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event57-15-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"(미사키. 무대에 올라온 건 다섯뿐이지만\n마음은 언제나 그대와 이어져 있다. 자, 같이 연주하자.\n오늘밤 별이 뜬 하늘보다도 눈부시게 빛나는 우리의 스테이지다……!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event57-15-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"(코코로 짱한테 용기를 받았던 일이 내 헬로해피의 시작.\n주위의 도움을 받기만 하던 나였지만\n모두와 함께하면서 조금씩 앞으로 나아갈 수 있었어.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event57-15-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"(코코로 짱처럼 될 순 없지만\n난 내가 할 수 있는 방법으로\n받은 용기를 모두한테 전해주고 싶어……!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event57-15-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미셸","body":"(온 세상을 웃는 얼굴로라니, 가능할 리가 없다고 생각했는데……\n정신 차려보니 나도 헬로해피의 주민이 될 줄은 몰랐네.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event57-15-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미셸","body":"(그치만 그것도 나쁘지 않다고 생각해.\n평범히나 적당한 것이 제일인 나라도 누군가를 웃는 얼굴로\n만들 수 있다고 말해준다면, 나도 거기에 응답해주고 싶으니까.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event57-15-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"즐거움은 혼자서는 생기지 않는 거야!\n누군가가 없으면 생기지 않는 근사한 기분이야!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event57-15-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"그러니까 만약 즐거워지고 싶다면\n곁에 있는 사람한테 당신의 즐거움을 전해줘!\n분명 당신 안에서도 즐거움이 생겨날 거야!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event57-15-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"만약 그래도 즐거워지지 않는 사람이 있다면 그때는……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event57-15-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"우리 헬로해피한테 맡겨줘!\n온 세상을 웃는 얼굴로 만드는 노래로 최고의 즐거움을 선물할게!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event57-15-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"방문객A","body":"좋은데, 스마일 놀이동산!\n이런 숨겨진 놀이동산이 있다니 몰랐어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"방문객B","body":"퍼레이드를 하는 밴드, 헬로해피라고 하는구나.\n다음에 라이브를 보러 가볼까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"미셸","body":"후~……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"m